    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/bef89229232326052cd0dcf63f2cf657.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/bef89229232326052cd0dcf63f2cf657.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/bef89229232326052cd0dcf63f2cf657.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/7b4527b355cc2b7fbac6eb0f8c4d0433.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/7b4527b355cc2b7fbac6eb0f8c4d0433.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/7b4527b355cc2b7fbac6eb0f8c4d0433.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/87e52a13735856579a9cc07a54bcbda2.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/87e52a13735856579a9cc07a54bcbda2.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/87e52a13735856579a9cc07a54bcbda2.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/46e6bc8ed05c19a18b6ed67c77f2c008.webp?t=1768389555\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/46e6bc8ed05c19a18b6ed67c77f2c008.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" class=\"bb_img\" width=780 height=392 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/c2bfe07842186cf3ff3f3fb7036b3994.avif?t=1768389555\" width=700 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">夜路上的社畜，唯一的快乐——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">手机，竟在瞬间被黑影夺走！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">随之而来的是自称“缘神”的戏谑低语：</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">「……想要实现，认识女孩子的梦想吗？」</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">红线缠绕的白兔，引你踏入诡异的鸟居。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">光芒炸裂、世界崩塌——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">当你回过神时，已身处一片陌生而冰冷的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">以及……一个满是血痕、看起来痛苦又寂寞的少女。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">——你，会勇敢伸出援手吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你的每一次选择，将改写「缘影」中的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你，真的能带领她们，抵达「彼岸」吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/78fc7be48db6ae42e042a0d1c6f76433.avif?t=1768389555\" width=700 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>灵符契合，破除诅咒</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">自由组合字卡，展开无限可能的解谜乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/35b05460dc0782daa5932303a9a6c457.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/35b05460dc0782daa5932303a9a6c457.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/35b05460dc0782daa5932303a9a6c457.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>多样小游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">迷你游戏不迷你，挑战你的反应与智慧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/193888ec5325dde95fc6e9ad3489fba0.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/193888ec5325dde95fc6e9ad3489fba0.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/193888ec5325dde95fc6e9ad3489fba0.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>萌萌少女动起来</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">猫耳、狐耳、兔耳少女全员登场，灵动的眼神、可爱的耳朵动个不停♡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/5a38bebf67d8b781e6ec464afd7de301.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/5a38bebf67d8b781e6ec464afd7de301.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/5a38bebf67d8b781e6ec464afd7de301.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>多样角色，命运交织</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">温柔体贴的傻姐姐、懦弱却勇敢的少女、自称神明的雌小鬼、温婉动人的贤慧幼妻——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你将与她们相遇、陪伴、抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/b1ab9273cc1c8518642eb1cb9759f29d.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/b1ab9273cc1c8518642eb1cb9759f29d.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/b1ab9273cc1c8518642eb1cb9759f29d.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>浓厚和风怪谈氛围</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">走进神秘的神社巫女世界，体验古老仪式、诡异祭典与潜藏的诅咒，逐步揭开被掩埋的真相......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/f5926ed1670bb627b1ec46c2cb3be99d.poster.avif?t=1768389555\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/f5926ed1670bb627b1ec46c2cb3be99d.webm?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/f5926ed1670bb627b1ec46c2cb3be99d.mp4?t=1768389555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146610/extras/e7c2238c0124ce5c9eb645e1a19f7b8b.avif?t=1768389555\" width=700 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏适合喜欢 <strong>阅读文字</strong> 来体验游戏的玩家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜过程需要根据文字描写来推理、观察，发挥你的 <strong>想象力</strong> 才能找到突破口。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若遇到困难，可使用「提示系统」获取关键线索，让体验更加顺畅。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏标签(TAGS) | <i>灵缘,靈緣,解謎,解谜,動漫,日系,神社,巫女,miko,猫耳,兽耳,日本,Love,恋爱,视觉小说,gal,galgame,avg,动漫,美少女,lsp,美女,制服,少女,cos,loli,萝莉,妹控,缘</i></p>",
